  yield emotional-arc ≡ "waiting → tension → recognition → peace → self-definition"

  yield scene-purpose ≡ "Resolution. The story's question ('what do you do when you discover your origin?') is answered: you make your origin part of your public identity. Theme crystallizes through action, not exposition."

